Hollywood, Toluca Lake, Universal City, Hollywood, Los Feliz, Silver Lake and 
the Hollywood Hills. MATT MOODY / Los Angeles Times ; Photo, Henry A. Waxman; 
Photo, John N. Cowles 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
