competition among 700 San Gabriel Valley contestants who vied for the title. 
Rullman, a San Marino High School senior and member of the varsity cheering 
squad, will be the 73rd Rose Queen. ; Photo, Dawn Gray, left, and Andrea Uyeda 
react to the announcement that Cara Payton Rullman, right, is named queen of 
the 1991 Tournament of Roses. IRIS SCHNEIDER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
