COUNTY SHERIFF'S DEPARTMENT; STING OPERATIONS; POLICE CORRUPTION; EMPLOYEE 
THEFT; MONEY LAUNDERING; TAX EVASION; EXTORTION; POLICE -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; 
DRUG TRAFFICKING -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY 
</P>
