Columbia, Md., Sept. 16. Wingate told police she had consented to have sex. 
</P>
<P>
A 21-year-old woman charged Wingate last month in a civil suit in San Antonio, 
alleging that he sexually assaulted her last June after drinking with her at a 
nightclub. 
