<P>
TOUCHWOOD PACIFIC PARTNERS I; WALT DISNEY CO; YAMAICHI GENERAL FINANCE CO; 
UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN INVESTMENTS -- JAPAN; MOTION PICTURE INDUSTRY -- 
UNITED STATES; LIMITED PARTNERSHIPS 
</P>
