CONTRIBUTIONS; ETHICS; CONFLICT OF INTEREST; LOBBYING; LOBBYISTS; SPECIAL 
INTEREST GROUPS; CALIFORNIA GOVERNOR; FEINSTEIN, DIANNE; FUND RAISING; 
POLITICAL CAMPAIGNS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
