NATIONAL PARKS; NATIONAL PARK SERVICE; GOVERNMENT REGULATION; ACQUISITIONS; 
CONCESSIONS; RIDENOUR, JAMES; MATSUSHITA ELECTRIC INDUSTRIAL CO LTD; WASSERMAN, 
LEW R; YOSEMITE PARK AND CURRY CO; YOSEMITE RESTORATION TRUST; 
